ih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT2sDqO.png&h=a6e3a5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落山決定行返大路落<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6s8nSB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6s8nSB.png&h=af0a3795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有蛋黃哥樣嘅山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tqy7Drb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqy7Drb.png&h=129e53f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天使光環雲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WxhPRMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxhPRMc.png&h=10aaa0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n魔鬼魚山丘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WuYWwMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuYWwMd.png&h=52806ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安全落到山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAy7Dre.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAy7Dre.png&h=f8b35e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人玩滑翔傘！應該係 我都想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8EEOnSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8EEOnSV.png&h=eac65a04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a5fc5352b2a7adbdf1c04e8ef6deb7502eec92e","tid":2497180,"uid":200361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0f7865ceea5287a3ca96b4b457ff0a5381abfba","tid":2497180,"uid":332128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"咁偏僻都有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"Yes芬蘭網絡覆蓋率差唔多100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828d6f8d85b78416ac0a4071edf94461e3c1